{
  "texts": [
    "Fig. 6 Educators' Responses Regarding Banning or Regulating the ChatGPT in Different Writing Domains",
    "Fourth, we asked about the allowable percentage of AI-generated text in faculty and students' written outputs.",
    "We listed four options: less than 10 percent, 10-15 percent, 16-25 percent, and 26-50 percent.",
    "Option b, 10-15 percent, was the most frequent response, with 39 respondents.",
    "This is followed by the first option, less than 10 percent, with 36 respondents."
  ]
}